# 🌟 PROMPTLY

A web and mobile app (Android & iOS) designed to simplify formatting and response types for Gemini prompts, aimed at users who write texts like articles, essays, and other written creations.

## 🚀 Technologies Used

- React (Web)  
- React Native (Android & iOS)
- Typescript

## ⚙️ Main Features

- Input of prompts
- List of format categories and their types

## 🛠 How to Run Locally

1. Clone the repository:  
git clone https://github.com/igortavares-code/promptly.git

2. Navigate to the project folder:  
cd promptly

3. Install dependencies:  npm install

4. Run on web: npm expo start

5. Open your browser at `http://localhost:19006` or use the Expo app on your phone.

## 🔨 Project Status

Core feature—prompt creation and formatting—is implemented. Additional features are under development.

